-- China May Increase Reserve Requirement for Banks, Securities Times Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-08-02T22:49:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/china-may-increase-reserve-requirement-for-banks-securities-times-reports.html

          
          
             China’s central bank in October may
increase the amount of reserves the nation’s banks are required
to keep, the Securities Times reported today, citing
unidentified officials from the banking industry.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Jian Guo Jiang in Shanghai at 
